# Gallery asset hygiene
#
# Large generated binaries are NOT committed here: validated runs produce them
# on VESSL (scripts/precompute_gallery_artifacts.py) and the large media are
# synced into the gitops repo separately (see gallery-deploy/DEPLOYMENT.md).
#
# Small samples ARE committed so the public pages render: PNG thumbnails,
# manifest.json, sparams.json, and small Touchstone files.

# --- ignore large generated media / volume files ---
*.mp4
*.webm
*.gif
*.npz
*.npy
*.vtk
*.vti
*.h5
*.hdf5

# --- but always allow the small committed samples ---
!.gitignore
!README.md
!**/manifest.json
!**/sparams.json
!**/*.png
!**/*.s1p
!**/*.s2p
!**/*.s3p
!**/*.s4p
